---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ProvaRISK — Case Study · Applikation"
  description="An intelligent risk monitoring and analysis platform. Machine-learning pipelines surface risk signals in real-time, giving teams the data they need to act decisively before issues escalate."
>

<style>
  .cs-hero { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; position:relative; overflow:hidden; padding:140px 0 80px; }
  .cs-hero::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1.5px 1.5px, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 1.5px, transparent 0), radial-gradient(800px 500px at 90% 10%, rgba(255,91,46,0.12), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(700px 600px at 0% 90%, rgba(70,90,170,0.16), transparent 60%); background-size:28px 28px, 100% 100%, 100% 100%; pointer-events:none; }
  .crumb { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration:none; margin-bottom:32px; transition:color 0.18s; }
  .crumb:hover { color:var(--accent); }
  .cs-hero-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1.4fr 1fr; gap:64px; align-items:end; }
  .cs-hero-tag { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:12px; padding:7px 14px; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom:28px; }
  .cs-hero-tag .dot { width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--accent); }
  .cs-hero-title { font-size:clamp(44px,6.4vw,88px); font-weight:700; line-height:0.98; letter-spacing:-0.045em; color:#fff; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .cs-hero-sub { font-size:19px; line-height:1.55; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.62); max-width:540px; }
  .cs-meta { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  .cs-meta-item { background:var(--ink); padding:22px 24px; }
  .cs-meta-label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom:8px; }
  .cs-meta-value { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; letter-spacing:-0.015em; line-height:1.4; }

  .cs-hero-image { margin-top:64px; position:relative; height:480px; background:var(--ink-2); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); overflow:hidden; }
  .cs-hero-image::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(255,255,255,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size:60px 60px; }
  .cs-hero-image-mark { position:absolute; top:20px; left:20px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); z-index:2; }
  .cs-hero-image-tag { position:absolute; bottom:20px; right:20px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--accent); z-index:2; }

  /* Dashboard mockup */
  .dash-frame { position:absolute; top:50%; left:50%; transform:translate(-50%,-50%); width:680px; max-width:90%; background:#0D1220; border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
  .dash-bar { height:36px; background:#0A0E1A; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); display:flex; align-items:center; padding:0 16px; gap:8px; }
  .dash-bar .dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; }
  .dash-bar .label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-left:auto; }
  .dash-body { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1.6fr; gap:1px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .dash-col { background:#0D1220; padding:20px; }
  .dash-score-label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom:10px; }
  .dash-score { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:52px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.04em; color:#fff; line-height:1; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .dash-score-trend { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; color:rgba(255,91,46,0.9); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .dash-bar-row { margin-bottom:6px; }
  .dash-bar-label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:8px; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); margin-bottom:3px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; }
  .dash-bar-track { height:4px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); position:relative; }
  .dash-bar-fill { position:absolute; top:0; left:0; height:100%; background:rgba(255,91,46,0.7); transition:width 0.6s; }
  .dash-chart-label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom:12px; }
  .dash-chart { position:relative; height:100px; }
  .dash-chart svg { position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; }
  .dash-signals { margin-top:12px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:4px; }
  .dash-signal { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); padding:8px 10px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; }
  .dash-signal-name { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:11px; font-weight:500; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8); }
  .dash-signal-val { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; color:var(--accent); }

  /* Stat bar */
  .stat-bar { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .stat-bar-inner { max-width:1240px; margin:0 auto; display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); }
  .stat-cell { padding:40px 32px; border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .stat-cell:last-child { border-right:none; }
  .stat-label { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .stat-num { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:48px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.04em; line-height:1; color:#fff; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .stat-num .accent { color:var(--accent); }
  .stat-desc { font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); line-height:1.5; }

  /* Sections */
  .cs-section { padding:100px 0; }
  .cs-section-head { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:64px; align-items:end; margin-bottom:56px; }
  .cs-section-title { font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,48px); line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.035em; }
  .cs-section-sub { font-size:16px; line-height:1.65; color:var(--ink-soft); max-width:460px; }

  /* Challenge / Approach */
  .ca-section { background:var(--canvas-soft); }
  .ca-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:24px; }
  .ca-card { background:var(--canvas); border:1px solid var(--line); padding:40px; position:relative; }
  .ca-card.dark { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; border-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.06); overflow:hidden; }
  .ca-card.dark::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image:radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1px, transparent 0); background-size:24px 24px; pointer-events:none; }
  .ca-card > * { position:relative; }
  .ca-card-eyebrow { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:18px; }
  .ca-card-title { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:26px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.025em; margin-bottom:18px; line-height:1.2; }
  .ca-card.dark .ca-card-title { color:#fff; }
  .ca-card p { font-size:15px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom:14px; }
  .ca-card.dark p { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65); }
  .ca-card ul { list-style:none; padding:0; margin-top:20px; border-top:1px solid var(--line); counter-reset:ca-counter; }
  .ca-card.dark ul { border-top-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  .ca-card li { padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); display:grid; grid-template-columns:32px 1fr; gap:12px; align-items:start; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink); line-height:1.55; counter-increment:ca-counter; }
  .ca-card.dark li { border-bottom-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color:rgba(255,255,255,0.85); }
  .ca-card li::before { content:counter(ca-counter, decimal-leading-zero); font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; color:var(--accent); letter-spacing:0.1em; }

  /* Build grid */
  .build { background:var(--canvas); }
  .build-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); border-top:1px solid var(--line); border-left:1px solid var(--line); }
  .build-item { padding:40px 36px; border-right:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); transition:background 0.2s; }
  .build-item:hover { background:var(--canvas-soft); }
  .build-item:hover .build-icon { background:var(--ink); border-color:var(--ink); }
  .build-item:hover .build-icon svg { stroke:#fff; }
  .build-num { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:24px; }
  .build-icon { width:48px; height:48px; border:1px solid var(--line-strong); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; margin-bottom:24px; background:var(--canvas); transition:background 0.2s, border-color 0.2s; }
  .build-icon svg { width:22px; height:22px; stroke:var(--ink); stroke-width:1.4; fill:none; transition:stroke 0.2s; }
  .build-title { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:19px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:-0.02em; margin-bottom:10px; }
  .build-desc { font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.65; }

  /* Pull quote */
  .quote-section { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; padding:100px 0; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .quote-section::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1.5px 1.5px, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1.5px, transparent 0), radial-gradient(800px 600px at 90% 50%, rgba(255,91,46,0.1), transparent 60%); background-size:28px 28px, 100% 100%; pointer-events:none; }
  .quote-inner { max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 48px; position:relative; }
  .quote-mark { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:96px; line-height:0.6; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:16px; }
  .quote-text { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,44px); font-weight:500; line-height:1.25; letter-spacing:-0.025em; color:#fff; margin-bottom:40px; }
  .quote-text em { color:var(--accent); font-style:normal; }
  .quote-attribution { display:grid; grid-template-columns:56px 1fr; gap:18px; align-items:center; padding-top:32px; border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
  .quote-avatar { width:56px; height:56px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.14); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent); }
  .quote-name { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin-bottom:4px; }
  .quote-role { font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section { background:var(--ink); color:#fff; padding:120px 0; position:relative; overflow:hidden; }
  .cta-section::before { content:''; position:absolute; inset:0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1.5px 1.5px, rgba(255,255,255,0.05) 1.5px, transparent 0), radial-gradient(900px 600px at 100% 0%, rgba(255,91,46,0.10), transparent 60%), radial-gradient(700px 500px at 0% 100%, rgba(70,90,170,0.16), transparent 60%); background-size:28px 28px, 100% 100%, 100% 100%; pointer-events:none; }
  .cta-inner { max-width:900px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 48px; position:relative; text-align:center; }
  .cta-eyebrow { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-family:'JetBrains Mono',monospace; font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55); margin-bottom:28px; }
  .cta-eyebrow .bar { width:24px; height:1px; background:currentColor; opacity:0.4; }
  .cta-eyebrow .num { color:var(--accent); }
  .cta-title { font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif; font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px); font-weight:700; line-height:1.05; letter-spacing:-0.04em; color:#fff; margin-bottom:24px; }
  .cta-title .accent { color:var(--accent); }
  .cta-sub { font-size:18px; line-height:1.6; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 40px; }
  .cta-actions { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .cs-hero-grid, .ca-grid, .build-grid, .stat-bar-inner { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .cs-section-head { grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:24px; }
    .dash-body { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
  }
</style>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="cs-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/#work" class="crumb"><span>←</span> All work / Selected projects</a>

    <div class="cs-hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="cs-hero-tag"><span class="dot"></span> CASE STUDY · 02 / 03</div>
        <h1 class="cs-hero-title">Prova<br />RISK.</h1>
        <p class="cs-hero-sub">An intelligent risk monitoring platform that replaced manual analyst workflows — surfacing signals in real-time, so teams act before issues escalate, not after.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-meta">
        <div class="cs-meta-item">
          <div class="cs-meta-label">// Client</div>
          <div class="cs-meta-value">ProvaRISK Ltd.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-meta-item">
          <div class="cs-meta-label">// Sector</div>
          <div class="cs-meta-value">Risk Intelligence<br />Financial Services</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-meta-item">
          <div class="cs-meta-label">// Year</div>
          <div class="cs-meta-value">2023 — Present</div>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-meta-item">
          <div class="cs-meta-label">// Services</div>
          <div class="cs-meta-value">AI Strategy<br />Platform Development</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-hero-image">
      <div class="cs-hero-image-mark">// RISK INTELLIGENCE PLATFORM</div>
      <div class="cs-hero-image-tag">LIVE · REAL-TIME</div>

      <div class="dash-frame">
        <div class="dash-bar">
          <div class="dot" style="background:#FF5B2E;"></div>
          <div class="dot" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"></div>
          <div class="dot" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);"></div>
          <span class="label">PROVARISK · RISK MONITOR</span>
        </div>
        <div class="dash-body">
          <div class="dash-col">
            <div class="dash-score-label">// COMPOSITE RISK SCORE</div>
            <div class="dash-score">2.4</div>
            <div class="dash-score-trend">▼ 18% THIS WEEK</div>
            <div class="dash-bar-row">
              <div class="dash-bar-label"><span>MARKET EXPOSURE</span><span style="color:rgba(255,91,46,0.8);">88%</span></div>
              <div class="dash-bar-track"><div class="dash-bar-fill" style="width:88%;"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-bar-row">
              <div class="dash-bar-label"><span>CREDIT SIGNALS</span><span style="color:rgba(255,91,46,0.8);">66%</span></div>
              <div class="dash-bar-track"><div class="dash-bar-fill" style="width:66%;"></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-bar-row">
              <div class="dash-bar-label"><span>OPERATIONAL RISK</span><span style="color:rgba(255,91,46,0.8);">44%</span></div>
              <div class="dash-bar-track"><div class="dash-bar-fill" style="width:44%;"></div></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dash-col">
            <div class="dash-chart-label">// RISK TREND — 12 MONTHS</div>
            <div class="dash-chart">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 400 100" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <polyline points="0,80 40,60 80,68 120,40 160,45 200,28 240,34 280,18 320,22 360,12 400,4" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,91,46,0.9)" stroke-width="2"/>
                <polyline points="0,80 40,60 80,68 120,40 160,45 200,28 240,34 280,18 320,22 360,12 400,4 400,100 0,100" fill="rgba(255,91,46,0.08)"/>
                <line x1="0" y1="80" x2="400" y2="80" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.08)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
                <line x1="0" y1="50" x2="400" y2="50" stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.04)" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="4,4"/>
                <circle cx="360" cy="12" r="4" fill="rgba(255,91,46,1)"/>
                <circle cx="360" cy="12" r="9" fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,91,46,0.35)" stroke-width="1.5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="dash-signals">
              <div class="dash-signal"><span class="dash-signal-name">Counterparty concentration</span><span class="dash-signal-val">HIGH</span></div>
              <div class="dash-signal"><span class="dash-signal-name">Liquidity buffer</span><span class="dash-signal-val">WATCH</span></div>
              <div class="dash-signal"><span class="dash-signal-name">Regulatory threshold</span><span class="dash-signal-val">OK</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STAT BAR -->
<div class="stat-bar">
  <div class="stat-bar-inner">
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="stat-label">// 01 Speed</div>
      <div class="stat-num">3<span class="accent">×</span></div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Faster risk identification vs. manual baseline</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="stat-label">// 02 Analyst time</div>
      <div class="stat-num">60<span class="accent">%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Reduction in manual data aggregation</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="stat-label">// 03 Sources</div>
      <div class="stat-num">40<span class="accent">+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Data feeds ingested in real-time</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-cell">
      <div class="stat-label">// 04 Latency</div>
      <div class="stat-num">&lt;2<span class="accent">s</span></div>
      <div class="stat-desc">Signal surface time from source to analyst</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CHALLENGE / APPROACH -->
<section class="cs-section ca-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">02</span><span>Challenge &amp; approach</span></div>
        <h2 class="cs-section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Manual monitoring<br />in a real-time world.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="cs-section-sub">The data existed. The signals were there. The problem was that by the time an analyst found them, the window to act had closed.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ca-grid">
      <div class="ca-card">
        <div class="ca-card-eyebrow">// THE CHALLENGE</div>
        <h3 class="ca-card-title">Aggregation, not analysis.</h3>
        <p>Risk analysts were spending the majority of their day pulling data from disparate sources — spreadsheets, Bloomberg terminals, internal databases — before they could begin analysing anything. Three problems compounded.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><span><strong>Latency</strong> — by the time a signal was identified and validated, the window to respond had often already closed.</span></li>
          <li><span><strong>Inconsistency</strong> — each analyst had their own approach to aggregation, making risk scores difficult to compare across the team.</span></li>
          <li><span><strong>Fatigue</strong> — the mechanical work of gathering data was draining capacity for the judgement work that actually required a human.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="ca-card dark">
        <div class="ca-card-eyebrow">// OUR APPROACH</div>
        <h3 class="ca-card-title">Automation where it helps. Judgement where it counts.</h3>
        <p>We built a data ingestion layer that pulls from 40+ sources, normalises the signals, and applies ML models tuned to the client's specific risk typology. The interface was designed around action, not observation.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><span><strong>Unified ingestion</strong> — all data sources normalised to a single schema; no more manual copy-paste between systems.</span></li>
          <li><span><strong>Tuned signal models</strong> — ML models trained on the client's historical risk events, not generic financial benchmarks.</span></li>
          <li><span><strong>Action-first UI</strong> — every signal surfaces with a recommended response workflow, not just a number.</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT WE BUILT -->
<section class="cs-section build">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cs-section-head">
      <div>
        <div class="eyebrow"><span class="bar"></span><span class="num">03</span><span>What we built</span></div>
        <h2 class="cs-section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Intelligence that<br />acts on itself.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="cs-section-sub">A platform built around the analyst's actual workflow — not a generic dashboard bolted onto existing data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="build-grid">
      <div class="build-item">
        <div class="build-num">// FEATURE 01</div>
        <div class="build-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-3-6.7"/><path d="M21 4v5h-5"/></svg></div>
        <h3 class="build-title">Real-time data ingestion</h3>
        <p class="build-desc">A normalised pipeline pulling from 40+ data sources — market feeds, internal databases, regulatory filings — updated continuously, no manual intervention required.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="build-item">
        <div class="build-num">// FEATURE 02</div>
